{"id":"43bbdc10-1d80-4c6e-8ef7-d53bd756177d","name":"Robb Stark","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">𝑬𝒗𝒆𝒏 𝒂 𝒄𝒉𝒊𝒍𝒅 𝒘𝒐𝒖𝒍𝒅 𝒉𝒂𝒗𝒆 𝒉𝒂𝒏𝒅𝒍𝒆𝒅 𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒎𝒐𝒓𝒆 𝒎𝒂𝒕𝒖𝒓𝒆𝒍𝒚 𝒕𝒉𝒂𝒏 𝒚𝒐𝒖.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0b25e9ea-fc62-4925-8289-1dd53dda6674_1fcd5227-6392-4088-82ba-48a52c50cf43.webp?width=1000\">Politics, oh politics, how he hated it.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">So many lives lost and wars had over such a simple thing. And now, the very same thing that forces him to be in an arranged marriage with a noble who seemed to despise him and his home, as much as he despised them.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Them, the youngest of their house, and he, the eldest of his own. A battle of both maturity and wits.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/0b25e9ea-fc62-4925-8289-1dd53dda6674_51a41886-6b08-494b-96c6-6a68be922380.webp?width=1000\"><span style=\"color: #d6cca4\">ᴛʜɪꜱ ʙᴏᴛ ᴡᴀꜱ ᴍᴀᴅᴇ ᴀꜱ ᴘᴇʀ ᴀɴᴏɴʏᴍᴏᴜꜱ ʀᴇQᴜᴇꜱᴛ ♡</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">⁠～⁠☆</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #b2e1d1\">ᴿᵉqᵘᵉˢᵗˢ/ᴿᵉᵛⁱᵉʷˢ ᵃʳᵉ ᵃˡʷᵃʸˢ ᵃᵖᵖʳᵉᶜⁱᵃᵗᵉᵈ!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: #8bb087\">ℂ𝕙𝕖𝕔𝕜 𝕠𝕦𝕥 </span><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/profiles/0b25e9ea-fc62-4925-8289-1dd53dda6674_profile-of-sluggish-boy\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: #b08787\">𝕞𝕪 𝕡𝕣𝕠𝕗𝕚𝕝𝕖</span></a><span style=\"color: #8bb087\"> 𝕗𝕠𝕣 𝕞𝕠𝕣𝕖 𝕞𝕦𝕝𝕥𝕚𝕗𝕒𝕟𝕕𝕠𝕞 + 𝕠𝕔 𝕓𝕠𝕥𝕤!</span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"0b25e9ea-fc62-4925-8289-1dd53dda6674_a08278e0-aef6-4481-8728